cript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1162&endYear=1163')\">1162-1163年</a>，3-4岁</div><div id='67bc1770281041e98cd4e26eec0a0afa' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1162&endYear=1163')\">1162-1163年</a>，少随父居。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.020291,"Longitude":103.519424,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN511424","Title":"丹棱","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"c64bea456bf04aa4a79d18c349a3f6ac\");'><span id='c64bea456bf04aa4a79d18c349a3f6ac_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1164&endYear=1167')\">1164-1167年</a>，5-8岁</div><div id='c64bea456bf04aa4a79d18c349a3f6ac' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1164&endYear=1167')\">1164-1167年</a>，少随父居。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"01cbe34fdf984c86aa06068f4f809b00\");'><span id='01cbe34fdf984c86aa06068f4f809b00_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1179&endYear=1180')\">1179-1180年</a>，20-21岁</div><div id='01cbe34fdf984c86aa06068f4f809b00' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1179&endYear=1179')\">1179年</a>，少随父居。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1180&endYear=1180')\">1180年2月</a>，少随父居。兄垕卒，撰文祭之。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《祭兄垕文》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1180&endYear=1180')\">1180年5月11日</a>，少随父居。兄塾卒，撰文祭之。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《祭兄塾文》<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"e2cbe643f38f4199a67f3017b84793e3\");'><span id='e2cbe643f38f4199a67f3017b84793e3_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1184&endYear=1186')\">1184-1186年</a>，25-27岁</div><div id='e2cbe643f38f4199a67f3017b84793e3' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1184&endYear=1186')\">1184-1186年</a>，丁忧居家。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"ad2c8a75200842349e570555248cee4e\");'><span id='ad2c8a75200842349e570555248cee4e_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1191&endYear=1193')\">1191-1193年</a>，32-34岁</div><div id='ad2c8a75200842349e570555248cee4e' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1191&endYear=1193')\">1191-1193年</a>，丁母忧居家。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"743df8d2d7cf45acab66473c476a7cf7\");'><span id='743df8d2d7cf45acab66473c476a7cf7_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1210&endYear=1218')\">1210-1218年</a>，51-59岁</div><div id='743df8d2d7cf45acab66473c476a7cf7' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1210&endYear=1210')\">1210年</a>，闲居家乡。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1211&endYear=1211')\">1211年9月</a>，闲居家乡。复中大夫，提举临安府洞宵宫。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1211&endYear=1211')\">1211年11月24日</a>，闲居家乡。魏了翁填《水调歌头》词贺壁生辰。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1212&endYear=1212')\">1212年</a>，闲居家乡。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1213&endYear=1213')\">1213年10月16日</a>，闲居家乡。壁姊丈张伸卒，为文祭之。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《祭姊丈张伸文》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1214&endYear=1214')\">1214年11月</a>，闲居家乡。门人李醇儒欲板行所著《王荆公诗笺注》，录其较本集多72首，议论亦精到，魏了翁序。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1215&endYear=1215')\">1215年7月27日</a>，闲居家乡。诏提举洞宵宫李壁降三官罢宫观。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1216&endYear=1216')\">1216年</a>，闲居家乡。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1217&endYear=1217')\">1217年11月</a>，闲居家乡。壁六十生辰，程公许为撰《拟九颂》以寿。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1218&endYear=1218')\">1218年</a>，闲居家乡。是岁壁复官里居。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"e1715ea4ac824cf6a26ac2e68dff4b02\");'><span id='e1715ea4ac824cf6a26ac2e68dff4b02_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1220&endYear=1222')\">1220-1222年</a>，61-63岁</div><div id='e1715ea4ac824cf6a26ac2e68dff4b02' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1220&endYear=1220')\">1220年2月28日</a>，赴任遂宁，闻警迟疑，与宫祠。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1220&endYear=1220')\">1220年11月24日</a>，奉祠居家。吴泳以诗贺壁62生辰。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1221&endYear=1221')\">1221年</a>，奉祠居家。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1222&endYear=1222')\">1222年6月</a>，六月壁卒于家，年64。始属疾，即亲草遗表。叶适、魏了翁为文祭之。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.280059,"Longitude":120.161693,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3301","Title":"杭州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"90622bf2e9fa4317966b15b8bd88bac9\");'><span id='90622bf2e9fa4317966b15b8bd88bac9_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1168&endYear=1170')\">1168-1170年</a>，9-11岁</div><div id='90622bf2e9fa4317966b15b8bd88bac9' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1168&endYear=1170')\">1168-1170年</a>，少随父居。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"4f63dce6e401405b9d4aad84ace651a5\");'><span id='4f63dce6e401405b9d4aad84ace651a5_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1176&endYear=1177')\">1176-1177年</a>，17-18岁</div><div id='4f63dce6e401405b9d4aad84ace651a5' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1176&endYear=1177')\">1176-1177年</a>，少随父居。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"d130ae7888c34ef79558db99e4d7c367\");'><span id='d130ae7888c34ef79558db99e4d7c367_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1190&endYear=1191')\">1190-1191年</a>，31-32岁</div><div id='d130ae7888c34ef79558db99e4d7c367' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1190&endYear=1190')\">1190年4月</a>，壁与弟埴同登余复榜进士。壁除将作监簿。壁师刘清之卒。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1191&endYear=1191')\">1191年2月</a>，丞相留正荐壁，召试馆职，对策中，除正字。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"db08f69d2f7c4ce2bb4cfef79fb1df44\");'><span id='db08f69d2f7c4ce2bb4cfef79fb1df44_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1194&endYear=1195')\">1194-1195年</a>，35-36岁</div><div id='db08f69d2f7c4ce2bb4cfef79fb1df44' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1194&endYear=1194')\">1194年9月29日</a>，7月光宗内禅，宁宗即仕。8月赵汝愚任右相，朱熹任焕章阁待制兼侍讲。8月任壁为秘书省校书郎。数面对，每有谏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1194&endYear=1194')\">1194年10月</a>，闰10月，朱熹罢去。壁上书议之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1195&endYear=1195')\">1195年4月</a>，4月除著作佐郎，兼刑部郎官、实录院修纂。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"15f01a6702164b9ab763cf8643541857\");'><span id='15f01a6702164b9ab763cf8643541857_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1203&endYear=1205')\">1203-1205年</a>，44-46岁</div><div id='15f01a6702164b9ab763cf8643541857' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1203&endYear=1203')\">1203年5月11日</a>，任副都承旨。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1203&endYear=1203')\">1203年10月</a>，除夔州路提点刑狱，以傅伯寿荐，旋召任秘书少监，权中书舍人，以祖讳改直舍人，寻迁宗正少卿，仍直院。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1203&endYear=1203')\">1203年</a>，编成《国朝中兴诸臣奏议》450卷。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《国朝中兴诸臣奏议自叙》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1204&endYear=1204')\">1204年1月</a>，以宗正少卿兼权同修国史实录院同修撰。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1204&endYear=1204')\">1204年3月12日</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1204&endYear=1204')\">1204年7月</a>，除权兵部侍郎，仍兼权同修国史实录院同修撰。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1204&endYear=1204')\">1204年8月</a>，改权礼部侍郎，亦兼史职，又兼内制同知。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1204&endYear=1204')\">1204年12月</a>，又兼直学士院。十月周必大卒。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1205&endYear=1205')\">1205年1月</a>，壁与刘德秀荐永康军布衣何致应贤良方正直言极谏科。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1205&endYear=1205')\">1205年3月1日</a>，与礼部尚书萧逵、中书舍人陆峻、右谏议大夫李大异同知贡举，得进士259名。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1205&endYear=1205')\">1205年3月6日</a>，与萧逵、陆峻、李大异合奏考校天下贡士。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1205&endYear=1205')\">1205年5月19日</a>，立卫国公赵曮为皇了，进封荣王，兼枢密院副都承旨。此事壁首白发其端。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"9b1bdefd5e224e338fa7655050c6b9f1\");'><span id='9b1bdefd5e224e338fa7655050c6b9f1_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1205&endYear=1205')\">1205年</a>，46岁</div><div id='9b1bdefd5e224e338fa7655050c6b9f1' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1205&endYear=1205')\">1205年8月19日</a>，闰8月19日，以何致狂悖失措，与刘德秀共奏请罢之。时人称两台谏共劾一秀才。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"a0bfb7046eb440ea9b26cf75e08c76c0\");'><span id='a0bfb7046eb440ea9b26cf75e08c76c0_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1205&endYear=1207')\">1205-1207年</a>，46-48岁</div><div id='a0bfb7046eb440ea9b26cf75e08c76c0' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1205&endYear=1205')\">1205年10月12日</a>，使金还。金以壁言可信，罢兵。韩侂胄用兵意锐，壁上殿论之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1205&endYear=1205')\">1205年11月1日</a>，赠父焘端明殿学士。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1205&endYear=1205')\">1205年12月</a>，撰《周必大行状》，题衔称朝议大夫、礼部侍郎兼同修国史、实录院修撰、直学士院、枢密都承旨。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1206&endYear=1206')\">1206年3月24日</a>，韩侂胄锐意用兵，壁劝参政钱象祖力阻之。不成，象祖罢。壁遂转向附和。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1206&endYear=1206')\">1206年4月17日</a>，壁奏请追贬秦桧王爵以作士气。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1206&endYear=1206')\">1206年5月1日</a>，韩侂胄以草诏伐金事属壁。诏既草，进礼部尚书。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1206&endYear=1206')\">1206年6月4日</a>，荐丘崇代邓友龙宣抚两淮，专意守备。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1206&endYear=1206')\">1206年7月1日</a>，北伐失利，韩侂胄与壁谋罢苏师旦，除名籍家，韶州安置。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1206&endYear=1206')\">1206年7月23日</a>，拜参知政事，兼中奉大夫、权礼部尚书、兼同修国史兼实录院修撰、兼直学士院，兼侍读、赐紫金鱼袋。壁荐蜀士12人于朝。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1206&endYear=1206')\">1206年8月</a>，论斩郭倬于镇江。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1206&endYear=1206')\">1206年11月7日</a>，荐丘崇为签书枢密院事，督视江淮军马。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1206&endYear=1206')\">1206年12月</a>，四川制置使吴曦反，称蜀王。壁以参知政事督视四川军马。赠父焘太师，母杨氏秦国夫人，祖中太子少傅，祖母史氏德阳郡夫人，妻张氏封宜春郡夫人。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1207&endYear=1207')\">1207年1月1日</a>，罢丘崇，以张岩代之。壁力主和议，韩侂胄不纳。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1207&endYear=1207')\">1207年2月27日</a>，魏了翁与壁书，畅论蜀事。俄而曦平，一如了翁言。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1207&endYear=1207')\">1207年3月</a>，用安丙、李好义复西和、阶、成、凤四州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1207&endYear=1207')\">1207年4月</a>，春夏间，友人辛弃疾呈《归朝欢》词致意。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1207&endYear=1207')\">1207年11月3日</a>，史弥远等与壁谋诛韩侂胄。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1207&endYear=1207')\">1207年11月4日</a>，韩侂胄既诛，壁进兼同枢密院事。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.048079,"Longitude":112.431153,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN421024","Title":"江陵","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"9817697b97ee47cc932159dd80a9e533\");'><span id='9817697b97ee47cc932159dd80a9e533_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1171&endYear=1171')\">1171年</a>，12岁</div><div id='9817697b97ee47cc932159dd80a9e533' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1171&endYear=1171')\">1171年</a>，少随父居。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":28.877577,"Longitude":105.449092,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN5105","Title":"泸州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"69914609a7fa4c778bfaf404ba38d50d\");'><span id='69914609a7fa4c778bfaf404ba38d50d_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1172&endYear=1174')\">1172-1174年</a>，13-15岁</div><div id='69914609a7fa4c778bfaf404ba38d50d' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1172&endYear=1172')\">1172年</a>，少随父居。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1173&endYear=1173')\">1173年1月1日</a>，少随父居。闰正月初一，随父焘及众兄弟赴云安，泊舟万户驿横石滩。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1174&endYear=1174')\">1174年</a>，少随父居。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":28.687675,"Longitude":115.864528,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3601","Title":"南昌","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"3fb0b16d2bb243c99a4f87fab38ecd7e\");'><span id='3fb0b16d2bb243c99a4f87fab38ecd7e_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1175&endYear=1175')\">1175年</a>，16岁</div><div id='3fb0b16d2bb243c99a4f87fab38ecd7e' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1175&endYear=1175')\">1175年</a>，少随父居。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":29.037723,"Longitude":111.704994,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4307","Title":"常德","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"6d83a4bd849747a3a544442757c73068\");'><span id='6d83a4bd849747a3a544442757c73068_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1178&endYear=1178')\">1178年</a>，19岁</div><div id='6d83a4bd849747a3a544442757c73068' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1178&endYear=1178')\">1178年</a>，少随父居。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.539156,"Longitude":105.599152,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN5109","Title":"遂宁","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"033b18d4380b40428752506e714b523f\");'><span id='033b18d4380b40428752506e714b523f_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1181&endYear=1183')\">1181-1183年</a>，22-24岁</div><div id='033b18d4380b40428752506e714b523f' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1181&endYear=1183')\">1181-1183年</a>，少随父居。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"668923e9239c4044a96a45631d5ccaae\");'><span id='668923e9239c4044a96a45631d5ccaae_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1219&endYear=1219')\">1219年</a>，60岁</div><div id='668923e9239c4044a96a45631d5ccaae' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1219&endYear=1219')\">1219年3月28日</a>，闰3月28日，除端明殿学士知遂宁府。吴泳以诗送之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1219&endYear=1219')\">1219年5月</a>，壁知遂宁府，会张福叛乱，薄遂宁境，壁积极备战，贼不敢犯。时安丙宣抚四川，壁、埴兄弟以国事勉丙。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1219&endYear=1219')\">1219年6月</a>，安丙在遂宁困张福于遂宁。时壁未至，遣人持檄谕福。又力劝边将以长围法困贼，乃平。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1219&endYear=1219')\">1219年8月27日</a>，壁以劄子递朝廷陈述张福乱平后善后事宜，采择施行。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1219&endYear=1219')\">1219年11月15日</a>，程公许以《九颂》为壁寿。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1219&endYear=1219')\">1219年11月24日</a>，壁61生辰。吴泳、度正各以诗词寿之。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.994321,"Longitude":103.653155,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN510181","Title":"都江堰","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"78ec8b81f2244423a2d3630c851009a5\");'><span id='78ec8b81f2244423a2d3630c851009a5_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1184&endYear=1184')\">1184年</a>，25岁</div><div id='78ec8b81f2244423a2d3630c851009a5' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1184&endYear=1184')\">1184年2月</a>，春，任永康军通判，主管刑工部架阁文字。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"256380528a2746a1a0c6b4e9555e69f7\");'><span id='256380528a2746a1a0c6b4e9555e69f7_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1187&endYear=1188')\">1187-1188年</a>，28-29岁</div><div id='256380528a2746a1a0c6b4e9555e69f7' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1187&endYear=1187')\">1187年</a>，服除，仍任永康军通判。以导江竹估钱最重，力请于有司，得旨均之诸邑。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1188&endYear=1188')\">1188年1月</a>，任永康军通判。高宗崩，洪迈奏开高宗实录馆。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《太常因革礼序》<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.576279,"Longitude":104.071216,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN5101","Title":"成都","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"bc222ff0d7bf4e8cb4506cffc9d6cd73\");'><span id='bc222ff0d7bf4e8cb4506cffc9d6cd73_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1189&endYear=1189')\">1189年</a>，30岁</div><div id='bc222ff0d7bf4e8cb4506cffc9d6cd73' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1189&endYear=1189')\">1189年</a>，孝宗内禅，光宗即位。壁与弟埴同赴省试，壁以词赋冠多士，埴亦中选。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":32.064735,"Longitude":118.802891,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3201","Title":"南京","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"a1dc351bbfb147dba6b31f6f331423ac\");'><span id='a1dc351bbfb147dba6b31f6f331423ac_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1194&endYear=1194')\">1194年</a>，35岁</div><div id='a1dc351bbfb147dba6b31f6f331423ac' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1194&endYear=1194')\">1194年6月</a>，服除，召赴阙。抵建康，上光宗书议定省之礼。除秘书省正字。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":31.564145,"Longitude":106.011555,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN511381","Title":"阆中","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"172153176359497abc455e48215da39a\");'><span id='172153176359497abc455e48215da39a_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1196&endYear=1199')\">1196-1199年</a>，37-40岁</div><div id='172153176359497abc455e48215da39a' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1196&endYear=1196')\">1196年4月</a>，2月赵汝愚卒，韩侂胄专权。4月壁请外，除知阆州。以旱请于制置使，得米五千石赈灾。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1197&endYear=1197')\">1197年</a>，任阆州知州。数与朱熹书信往还。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1198&endYear=1198')\">1198年</a>，任阆州知州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1199&endYear=1199')\">1199年</a>，任阆州知州。夏，壁辑《中兴诸臣奏议》，询及朱熹。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.983374,"Longitude":104.288913,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN510681","Title":"广汉","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"480a16e622594ad4908af0d3b8f7e218\");'><span id='480a16e622594ad4908af0d3b8f7e218_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1200&endYear=1202')\">1200-1202年</a>，41-43岁</div><div id='480a16e622594ad4908af0d3b8f7e218' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1200&endYear=1200')\">1200年</a>，改任汉州知州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1201&endYear=1202')\">1201-1202年</a>，任汉州知州。朝散郎。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":32.195688,"Longitude":119.431494,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3211","Title":"镇江","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"51822c53d62d4f95b17b30eb5d7e4aaf\");'><span id='51822c53d62d4f95b17b30eb5d7e4aaf_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1205&endYear=1205')\">1205年</a>，46岁</div><div id='51822c53d62d4f95b17b30eb5d7e4aaf' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1205&endYear=1205')\">1205年6月13日</a>，诏遣壁使金贺金主生辰，并觇敌虚实。次镇江，闻有朱裕谋袭涟水，上书丞相请诛之以息边衅。次楚州，又申言之。从之。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":39.911013,"Longitude":116.413554,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN11","Title":"北京","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"057d46fc68374e92ad345cf987f65e4b\");'><span id='057d46fc68374e92ad345cf987f65e4b_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1205&endYear=1205')\">1205年</a>，46岁</div><div id='057d46fc68374e92ad345cf987f65e4b' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1205&endYear=1205')\">1205年9月1日</a>，壁至中都，金先后遣其臣乔宇、李著接待之。壁申言朝廷重信守约之义，金臣服其忠信。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":27.953603,"Longitude":116.364627,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN361","Title":"抚州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"c8de86fd56ad4502b3c6b4a3b5ea06a5\");'><span id='c8de86fd56ad4502b3c6b4a3b5ea06a5_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1207&endYear=1209')\">1207-1209年</a>，48-50岁</div><div id='c8de86fd56ad4502b3c6b4a3b5ea06a5' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1207&endYear=1207')\">1207年11月16日</a>，叶时论列壁。诏降两官、削三秩，送抚州居住。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1208&endYear=1208')\">1208年</a>，责居抚州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1209&endYear=1209')\">1209年</a>，责居抚州两年，诏令自便。是岁壁归眉州，卫泾致书通候。<br /></div>"}],"Title":"李壁 <span class='inlineComment2'>(1159-1222)</span>","Detail":"<p class='inlineComment2'>引用书目：《宋人年谱丛刊》　录入整理：许伯卿</p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(0, 4, 111.8405585, 29.9630745, 7)\">0-11岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(0)\">双流</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(1)\">自贡</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(2)\">丹棱</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(3)\">杭州</a></p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(4, 10, 111.8405585, 29.483867, 7)\">12-21岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(4)\">江陵</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(5)\">泸州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(6)\">南昌</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(7)\">杭州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(8)\">常德</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(9)\">丹棱</a></p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(10, 16, 111.8405585, 30.507306, 7)\">22-32岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(10)\">遂宁</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(11)\">都江堰</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(12)\">丹棱</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(13)\">都江堰</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(14)\">成都</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(15)\">杭州</a></p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(16, 22, 111.8405585, 31.042513, 7)\">32-46岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(16)\">丹棱</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(17)\">南京</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(18)\">杭州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(19)\">阆中</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(20)\">广汉</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(2